WEBVTT

00:00.047 --> 00:01.577
Previously on "The Family."

00:01.577 --> 00:04.030
- I'd like to order that cake.
- I'm just gonna grab the box.

00:04.030 --> 00:05.705
- I'll eat it here.
- Okay.

00:05.705 --> 00:06.897
Enjoy.

00:06.898 --> 00:10.083
- I paid a fine, I registered...
- Then they're gonna see this...

00:10.084 --> 00:11.258
Please turn it off.

00:11.283 --> 00:12.821
You're the one that likes it,
'cause they're so little.

00:12.822 --> 00:13.736
Enough!

00:13.737 --> 00:16.106
It's gonna stop now,
you sleeping with my husband.

00:16.107 --> 00:17.254
Do you think you're special?

00:17.255 --> 00:18.605
You wouldn't believe how many women

00:18.606 --> 00:20.715
take their panties off
for the dad who lost his son.

00:20.716 --> 00:23.605
I think he's lonely.
I think he misses him.

00:23.606 --> 00:24.735
I know how to get him.

00:24.736 --> 00:26.704
We'll be done with it, and you
can move on with your lives.

00:26.705 --> 00:27.606
How?

00:27.607 --> 00:29.655
I need to use Adam as bait.

00:29.656 --> 00:32.415
- Danny's not home.
- I left something up in his room.

00:32.415 --> 00:35.305
- She's a reporter.
- She's a blogger.

00:35.367 --> 00:36.515
This is Adam's room.

00:36.516 --> 00:38.102
I know who you are.

00:38.706 --> 00:41.593
Gus. Paternity test.
I got the results back.

00:41.594 --> 00:43.636
It's not him.

00:46.636 --> 00:48.369
Being alone changes you.

00:48.409 --> 00:50.314
_

00:51.636 --> 00:54.175
Come! Touch. All right.

00:54.176 --> 00:56.810
