22:47.079 --> 22:49.249
Please go away.

22:49.968 --> 22:52.070
You missed a lot of action today.

22:54.143 --> 22:55.366
What happened?

22:55.640 --> 23:00.620
Well, crawl out from under your
desk and maybe I'll tell you.

23:06.091 --> 23:07.581
